- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper's focus on machine learning and regression tasks falls under the scope of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes a non-iterative spectral algorithm for jointly recovering the common and local components in low rank multitask regression, which falls under the scope of data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.ST (Statistics): The paper's focus on regression tasks and sample complexity falls under the scope of statistics.
